    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《星界战士》与《黑暗献祭》的开发团队倾力呈现：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款全新的俯视角动作角色扮演游戏，采用精美的手绘像素艺术打造，带来史诗般激烈的战斗体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸于支离破碎的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/6ca42491f1a12f4fd976fa18aaab6728.poster.avif?t=1764344688\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/6ca42491f1a12f4fd976fa18aaab6728.webm?t=1764344688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/6ca42491f1a12f4fd976fa18aaab6728.mp4?t=1764344688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水晶从天而降，撕裂泰勒斯大陆，释放出神秘生物与毁灭之力。这片曾由魔法塑造的世界，如今面临崩溃，城市化为废墟，异样的力量肆意蔓延。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为求生存，人类与魔法生物融合，创造出强大战士。探索这个濒临崩溃的世界，揭开隐秘真相，为仅存的一切而战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>美丽却满目疮痍的土地，等待你去探索</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >泰勒斯大陆风光摄人心魄，却也满布废墟、苦难与阴暗中的谜团。自由穿行于广袤的大地——从绵延平原到要塞堡垒，从炽热沙漠到被遗忘的古老遗迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以奔跑、如狼般疾行、用钩索抵达难以触及之地，亦可攀上高处俯瞰整个世界。无数奥秘静待发掘。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为命运的主宰...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/bbfcfe2cf525d77538ace73e0f4e9642.poster.avif?t=1764344688\" width=800 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/bbfcfe2cf525d77538ace73e0f4e9642.webm?t=1764344688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/bbfcfe2cf525d77538ace73e0f4e9642.mp4?t=1764344688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演一对英雄搭档：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>阿尔文</strong>：一位以猎杀暗影为生的人类游侠，渴求获得更强大的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>凯特</strong>：一位初次踏入现实世界、对一切一无所知的以太体生命。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>...打破命定之局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/2c1a5ff841eee9f36b58928d6ad6160c.poster.avif?t=1764344688\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/2c1a5ff841eee9f36b58928d6ad6160c.webm?t=1764344688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/2c1a5ff841eee9f36b58928d6ad6160c.mp4?t=1764344688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >依照你的战斗风格定制并升级两位英雄的物理与魔法技能，体验兼具深度机制与自由操控的流畅战斗。锻造强力升级道具，依照你的方式构筑专属流派，突破重重挑战，揭开等待昭示的真相。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一体双魂</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/fbd00e4391a209b628a70a2390afbbd6.avif?t=1764344688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras_big/fbd00e4391a209b628a70a2390afbbd6.avif?t=1764344688 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学会共生，是挑战的一部分——也是解锁真正力量的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索内心领域，培育灵魂与肉体的羁绊。驾驭以太魔法，唤醒被遗忘的记忆，蜕变为更强大的自己。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>诸命归一途</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中你会遇到许多令人难忘的角色——有忠实的伙伴，也有危险的敌人。 <br>每个角色都有专属的配音、各自的使命和待你发掘的故事。 <br>这些剧情将通过精美的像素动画演绎，绝对会给你留下深刻印象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/f9180d1409378bd37ad2439d4f3244b7.poster.avif?t=1764344688\" width=640 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/f9180d1409378bd37ad2439d4f3244b7.webm?t=1764344688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276270/extras/f9180d1409378bd37ad2439d4f3244b7.mp4?t=1764344688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Fallen Fates》讲述了一段命运交织、夙愿相左与取舍两难的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
